---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Running Coach"
  description="Privacy policy for Running Coach."
  pathname="/privacy"
>
  <article class="shell page page--privacy">
    <section class="hero-card">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        This page explains what data Running Coach uses, why it uses it, and how you can
        ask questions, disconnect a provider, or request deletion.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="policy-grid">
      <section class="policy-card">
        <h2>Who this applies to</h2>
        <p>
          This policy applies to people who connect their training data to Running Coach
          or use its website and connected services.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-card">
        <h2>What data Running Coach collects</h2>
        <p>
          Running Coach collects the account and training data needed to provide its
          service. This may include basic account details, activity history, training
          metrics, and connection details needed to keep linked services working.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-card">
        <h2>Why this data is used</h2>
        <p>
          Running Coach uses this data to review recent training, generate planning
          guidance, maintain connected integrations, and support basic troubleshooting.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-card">
        <h2>Connected providers</h2>
        <p>
          Running Coach may connect to third-party services such as Intervals to access
          training data you choose to share. Those services also have their own terms and
          privacy policies.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-card policy-card--wide card--status">
        <h2>Storage and retention</h2>
        <p>
          Running Coach stores the data needed to operate the service and maintain
          connected integrations. Data is kept only for as long as it is needed for
          product operation, account continuity, legal obligations, or user-requested
          support.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-card policy-card--wide card--info">
        <h2>How data is shared</h2>
        <p>
          Running Coach does not sell personal data. Data may be processed by service
          providers that are needed to host, secure, and operate the service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-card">
        <h2>Your choices</h2>
        <p>
          You can ask to disconnect a provider, request deletion of your data, or ask
          privacy questions using the contact information below.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-card">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For privacy questions, deletion requests, or provider disconnection requests,
          contact:
        </p>
        <p><strong>[contact email]</strong></p>
      </section>

      <section class="policy-card footer-spacer">
        <h2>Effective date</h2>
        <p>Effective date: [publish date]</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
